de.ovgu.wdok.guinan

Class GuinanResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ovgu.wdok.guinan.GuinanResult
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GuinanClientResult, GuinanStackoverflowResult, GuinanYoutubeResult

    public class GuinanResult
extends java.lang.Object
    Result object for the Guinan connectors, wrapping results from connector's Web API into a common result object.
    The results from a connector are Web resources, described through their URI, title, tags, etc.

    This class represents basically just data objects with getters and setters, but it doesn't contain any logic of its own.
    Version:
    0.6
    Author:
    Katrin Krieger
